<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= typeof isTrial !== 'undefined' && isTrial ? 'Trial Started' : 'Complete Your Payment' %> - MIGS List</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <style>
    .success-page {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #dcfce7 100%);
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    .success-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .success-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .success-header .check-icon {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      background: #16a34a;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: white;
    }
    .success-header h1 {
      color: #166534;
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .success-header p {
      color: #4b5563;
    }
    .success-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    .success-card h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: #1f2937;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .trial-box {
      background: #dcfce7;
      border: 2px solid #86efac;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .trial-box h3 {
      color: #166534;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
    .trial-box p {
      color: #15803d;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .trial-days {
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #16a34a;
      display: block;
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
    }
    .payment-box {
      background: #fef3c7;
      border: 2px solid #f59e0b;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .payment-box h3 {
      color: #92400e;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }
    .payment-details {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 1rem;
    }
    .payment-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0.5rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
    }
    .payment-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }
    .payment-row .label {
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .payment-row .value {
      color: #1f2937;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .etransfer-email {
      background: #1e40af;
      color: white;
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 1rem 0;
      word-break: break-all;
    }
    .payment-option {
      background: #f8fafc;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin: 1.5rem 0;
    }
    .payment-option h3 {
      margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
      color: #1e293b;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    .mailing-address {
      background: #1e40af;
      color: white;
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }
    .steps-list {
      margin: 1.5rem 0;
    }
    .steps-list li {
      padding: 0.75rem 0;
      padding-left: 2rem;
      position: relative;
      color: #374151;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
    }
    .steps-list li:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .steps-list li::before {
      content: attr(data-step);
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      width: 1.5rem;
      height: 1.5rem;
      background: #2563eb;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .note-box {
      background: #f0f9ff;
      border: 1px solid #bae6fd;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
    .note-box h4 {
      color: #0369a1;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
    }
    .note-box p {
      color: #0c4a6e;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .nav-simple {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .nav-simple a {
      color: #16a34a;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .footer-link {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
    .footer-link a {
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .login-btn {
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
      background: #16a34a;
      color: white;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
    .login-btn:hover {
      background: #15803d;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="success-page">
  <div class="success-container">
    <nav class="nav-simple">
      <a href="/">MIGS List</a>
    </nav>

<% if (typeof isTrial !== 'undefined' && isTrial) { %>
    <div class="success-header">
      <div class="check-icon">✓</div>
      <h1>Your Trial is Active!</h1>
      <p>You can now log in and start using MIGS List</p>
    </div>

    <div class="success-card">
      <div class="trial-box">
        <h3>Free Trial</h3>
        <span class="trial-days">30</span>
        <p>days remaining</p>
      </div>

      <h2>What's Next?</h2>
      <ol class="steps-list">
        <li data-step="1">Log in with the email and password you just created</li>
        <li data-step="2">Create units/sectionals to organize your members</li>
        <li data-step="3">Add members and upload their signed documents</li>
        <li data-step="4">Export member lists to Excel anytime</li>
      </ol>

      <a href="/login" class="login-btn">Log In Now</a>

      <div class="note-box">
        <h4>After Your Trial</h4>
        <p>Continue using MIGS List for just $500/year (first year) or $800/year after. We'll remind you before your trial ends.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="note-box">
        <h4>Questions?</h4>
        <p>Contact us anytime at support@migslist.com</p>
      </div>
    </div>
<% } else { %>
    <div class="success-header">
      <div class="check-icon">✓</div>
      <h1>Request Received!</h1>
      <p>Complete your payment to activate your account</p>
    </div>

    <div class="success-card">
      <div class="payment-box">
        <h3>Payment Required</h3>
        <div class="payment-details">
          <div class="payment-row">
            <span class="label">Subscription</span>
            <span class="value">Annual (1 year)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="payment-row">
            <span class="label">Amount Due</span>
            <span class="value">$500.00 CAD</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>Payment Options</h2>

      <div class="payment-option">
        <h3>Option 1: Interac e-Transfer (Fastest)</h3>
        <div class="etransfer-email">payments@migslist.com</div>
        <ol class="steps-list">
          <li data-step="1">Log in to your online banking</li>
          <li data-step="2">Select Interac e-Transfer</li>
          <li data-step="3">Send <strong>$500.00 CAD</strong> to <strong>payments@migslist.com</strong></li>
          <li data-step="4">In the message field, include your <strong>Union Local name</strong></li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="payment-option">
        <h3>Option 2: Cheque by Mail</h3>
        <p>Make cheque payable to: <strong>Migs List</strong></p>
        <p>Include your <strong>Union Local name</strong> on the cheque or in a note.</p>
        <div class="mailing-address">
          Migs List<br>
          9880 Ridge Road<br>
          Windsor, Ontario<br>
          Canada N8R 1G6
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="note-box">
        <h4>What happens next?</h4>
        <p>Once we receive your payment, we'll activate your account and send login credentials to the admin email you provided. e-Transfers are typically processed within 1-2 business days. Cheques may take 5-7 business days after receipt.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="note-box">
        <h4>Questions?</h4>
        <p>If you have any questions about your signup or payment, please contact us at support@migslist.com</p>
      </div>
    </div>
<% } %>

    <div class="footer-link">
      <a href="/">Return to homepage</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
